name: Freeland
summary: Freeland is a virtual universe waiting to be explored, conquered, and shaped by your choices in this massively multiplayer online role-playing adventure. Immerse yourself in a colossal VRMMORPG where expansive open worlds teem with endless possibilities. Engage in quests that will challenge and reward you as you traverse this ever-evolving virtual universe. Unveil the rich storyline and forge your identity while connecting with players from across the globe through unparalleled social experiences.
